  <class_name>SetBuildingToConstructionSet</class_name>
  <display_name>Set Building To Construction Set</display_name>
  <description>This measures changes the building's default construction set to one selected by the user from a list of available default construction sets.</description>
  <modeler_description>No checking of any sorts is performed. The available default construction sets are obtained via the constructionset = SELECTFROM(model.getDefaultConstructionSets) method and the seleted construction set is applied via the building = model.getBuilding and building.setDefaultConstructionSet(constructionset) methods.</modeler_description>
